    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)))
    v0 = (0.18 - 0.14)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.42) - 0.53) + ((v2 + 0.72 * v0 + 0.47) + (v0 + 0.02 / tmp + 0.78)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.35)) * ((v0 + 0.04 - v2 + 0.01) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.18)))
    v0 = v0
